OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be cloudy as bands of
OL,6,Frain push northeast in the morning.
OL,7,FRain will turn showery later, these
OL,8,Fshowers heavy and thundery at times.
OL,9,FWindy at times, especially around the
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers or longer spells of
OL,13,Frain spread in through the evening and
OL,14,Fovernight, the rain heavy at times.
OL,15,FWindy around the coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
