OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FShowers occasionally forming
OL,6,Flonger spells of rain in the morning,
OL,7,Fheavy and thundery at times. Becoming
OL,8,Fdrier and brighter through the
OL,9,Fafternoon as showers fade away. Windy
OL,10,Fat times.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA band
OL,13,Fof rain pushes east Friday with
OL,14,Fshowers following later. Bright spells
OL,15,Fand showers on Saturday. Dry and
OL,16,Fbright on Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
